
# Tehreem Anwar – UX Research Portfolio

This is a React-based personal portfolio site styled with TailwindCSS.

## Features
- Responsive layout and smooth scroll
- Handwritten quote and professor recommendation
- Embedded PDF resume viewer
- Contact form powered by Formspree
- Clean aesthetic using serif/sans font pairing

## To Deploy on Vercel
1. [Sign up for Vercel](https://vercel.com)
2. Connect your GitHub account
3. Push this project to a new GitHub repo
4. Import it on Vercel → Done!

Enjoy your live UX portfolio!

–– Tehreem Anwar
